title: Dawson's Market
description: Organic grocery store/cafe in the Rockville Town Square. Has clearly marked vegan items in the salad bar and hot bar. Made-in-house vegan caesar and ranch dressings available. Try the vegan potato salad and chocolate cake. Also has a coffee/tea/juice bar, bulk food, produce, deli, beer/wine, bakery, frozen, and eat-in area. Free parking or small discount if you walk to store.
